{"tid":1424800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於”民間記者會”, 作為小小地做過公關, 有幾點建議比未來同類EVENT","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T17:47:36.000Z","uid":39412,"like":137,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"483ede4c2f1990307129ba22b645f3d8445ca0d9","tid":1424800,"uid":39412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n未講正題前首先背十次: 記者會講到頭其實都係點SPIN點SET AGENDA</strong><br />\n<br />\n人邊個冇BIASE?成見? 話冇都係呃你, 記者一樣, 兩個月來時態呢度好多人會有種&rdquo;記者大多數, 即使唔係全部, 都同情我地&rdquo;的感覺, 不過可以講比大家知, 一定唔係, 你放料, 佢&rdquo;睇情況編輯&rdquo;再出, 全香港人不可能同時現場聽你講, 點都係&rdquo;食二手飯&rdquo;, 你點現場控制訊息好關鍵.<br />\n<br />\n點叫&rdquo;持平&rdquo;, 十個人有十種認知, 冇一種&rdquo;持平&rdquo;係大多數人都接受, 做到80%持平已經唔錯.<br />\n<br />\n記實後, 點冇大台都好, 都需要有一個TEAM準備材料, 包括聲明, SOUNDBITE, 回應口徑<br />\n<br />\n當年老細講明, 開得PRESS EVENT, 一定要大家有清晰目的<br />\n<br />\n好似可以定調為:<br />\n<strong>&rdquo;三位(或N位)有親歷近日活動參與者, 以第一身經歷披露多日心路歷程(舉例), 我唔代表所有人, 只就自己所見同傳媒朋友&rdquo;分享</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>現在政府正式開動公關機器, 就係要將戴黃帽全黑妖魔化, 你地要做就係反制, 比番媒介一個有血有肉面孔</strong><br />\n可以冇大台, 但決定正式記者會就都要有一組人在背後做MEDIA TEAM<br />\n工作如下：<br />\n１．擬定聲明，用番會出來見記者幾位朋友自己名義，就你可披露自己個人身份程度來分享自己心聲<br />\n２．度下ＳＯＵＮＤＢＩＴＥ， 一Ｄ吸引到媒介引用甚至做標題句子，好似 &quot;齊上齊落，為香港自由未來奮鬥;由反送中起，到鞏固民主為止&quot; `之類<br />\n3. 當然你地唔會好似商業機構拍公關公司，有固定media manager，但每次最好都有幾位代表，負責聯絡記者，同記者溝通，人可以次次不同，但呢個位一定要有，亦可以晌保障出記者會同道私隱前提下代表佢地同記者聯繫<br />\n<br />\n既然全球賣廣告都做到，搵幾位冇參與前面，唔驚會隨時被拉的面孔出現，可以做到比一個面孔比媒介睇, the business of PR is about perception, 入行鬼婆老細格言<br />\n<br />\n然後就係Media training，你唔可以到個日先膽粗粗上場等記者問，預先度晒有可能出現問題，再搵其他人幫手操一次，包括最冒犯性最難聽的問題，反覆度好最見得人答案，呢步不能不做，否則在記者媒介前好易出事<br />\n<br />\n到左個日，最好有一位可以出樣的做MC，引導流程再安排記者問問題，近來咁多直播，睇多幾次就應該識，不多講<br />\n<br />\n今次見大家比人挑戰代表性問題，既然係心聲分享，就守實我地只係分享個人所見，不代表全部示威者的底線，777都係咁然硬守條 line，再問就話因為我地兩個月來太多感想，想由第一身身份同公眾講說話<br />\n<br />\n同場最好有同伴負責全程錄音，呢種係標準記者會動作，以防比人亂寫或曲解<br />\n<br />\n現在網絡咁發達，當然網上不會有一個示威者&quot;官網&quot;，但可以同步制作自已一方角度影片，經個人或其他渠道發放分享，可以同時平衡傳統媒介報導，要同步<br />\n<br />\n記者會後唔係就咁算數，今次負責媒介的&quot;文宣&quot;最好電郵比出席記者感謝佢地出席，如果可行重可以留低聯絡方式比佢地續問，咁先至係禮成，如果之後可以有人keep不同報導反映內容角度更佳<br />\n<br />\n小小心得，唔知大家用唔用得著<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------"},{"pid":"5cedf24d359db87a61b06765810e9bd33dfec10b","tid":1424800,"uid":291279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11de1f68a76363ed61320f670a5767f514889489","tid":1424800,"uid":270489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"推比搞手們見到"},{"pid":"f5491f76d8e9d0e57b2b4d8c9d12c7de39148216","tid":1424800,"uid":258602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fe5a57b25d19f659175d889a401e78ce19294b48","tid":1424800,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:38:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0471d913c9edd543e19515dd182d0619ff8f382","tid":1424800,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc8eac230ffdfd818ffebf23dbdebac99e6862f5","tid":1424800,"uid":196494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb74a1ff0cd5d45dca02bad65466a76a0f37456d","tid":1424800,"uid":275607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8014e601fa16c84767fa467d361ec9481ea675d","tid":1424800,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"值得參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b1a8136fee281874f77d78623a2fadbbc22466","tid":1424800,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5cf771ced7114f3d80960389bcdfd934da136097","tid":1424800,"uid":184566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0459d017b8dafee01fd55e5faf6a83b676b2174","tid":1424800,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae69cccd32c55472994179a9d7ed1b652534a9cf","tid":1424800,"uid":297035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"90dc11db712cac5350ed20e0b879f445c67a9fa5","tid":1424800,"uid":144865,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:41:58.000Z","msg":"同埋唔該training 一training D人嘅public speaking.<br />\n講嚴肅野唔好笑，麻煩入一入mood 先，盡量講野前背熟先出街。<br />\n<br />\n利申：做緊PR"},{"pid":"ddb9c4c67e1f49cc0c8b15b765c8a8b92d16d266","tid":1424800,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494cc524ce8b3001d447e7de3ac4fd05d1dd67c6","tid":1424800,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09c202ca84517640fcc57c1b79041aa0e00e8515","tid":1424800,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"好文必推"},{"pid":"62d40c480277d0006d09f8f66abba6410a4ee3f8","tid":1424800,"uid":141354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd669bd2a772196cbc1292f58b4631dd8d5e22e2","tid":1424800,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"pish到啲人見到"},{"pid":"12352c7dcb716932d3eef569114c476dc531eeaf","tid":1424800,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"希望手足睇睇, 有用"},{"pid":"ac2bfb322e0beda7595ddc04f0991dc5ddb95ac7","tid":1424800,"uid":190332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:44:48.000Z","msg":"值得參考<br />\npush<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c84f6c284a1f200b02b0a7d88bbeb83d3f0658a","tid":1424800,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:45:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"94564ce8133a25730d2223e1edf7adf19c7502ba","tid":1424800,"uid":173552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:46:38.000Z","msg":"好值得參考同去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d280416fdda7b29c8e62cae028b7834d64865b11","tid":1424800,"uid":136249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:48:21.000Z","msg":"其實建議讀聲明最好背下稿先 望多d camera..同埋 可能收音問題，好似好細聲咁"},{"pid":"eca959f4ec5ef0714275255650fa298edee9196f","tid":1424800,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:49:10.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"57ae71b4856fa0c493884302cb4ea67994d5f1f9","tid":1424800,"uid":124696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d90c868cebbb2c746602cbf02f818c8a91ea4bca","tid":1424800,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:54:41.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"9712dbfc46592ff80fa2702fe7af15b301510143","tid":1424800,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:56:06.000Z","msg":"正經post 推"},{"pid":"e996ef36af98da559182169bc6ce1fff8d1f10a9","tid":1424800,"uid":39412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:56:28.000Z","msg":"回頭補充，現在好多人對&quot;示威者&quot;印象就係一群黃帽黑衣神秘人物，好似突然間出現，冇跟足咁耐新聞，係冇人會知大概係乜人，好似一群突然從天而降的唔知邊路人物<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為我誇張，係有好多人咁睇<br />\n<br />\n下次可以晌無需透露太多個人背景前提下，描繪下你見到的同道，可能係學生，父母，小工人，甚至可能係銀髮族(唔知有冇)，比人大概知原來一班咁平凡背景的人會因咁大目的，兩個月間由平凡人突然變成勇武，反映番為乜咁大決心<br />\n<br />\n都係個句，it is about perception, 現在既然大家講文宣戰，媒介就係要有血有肉的故事，網上面書見好多，推去比傳統媒介一樣緊要<br />\n<br />\n唔一定要學梁繼平咁除口罩，但大概輪廓要比大家知"},{"pid":"60eaf590ef99e28ea579df0420084533763c0d9b","tid":1424800,"uid":272667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:59:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dec797fdbcf9f567328bd41cf54089759249bfc1","tid":1424800,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:01:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825e05a52097e528460533a2f2340a2a6648917b","tid":1424800,"uid":20834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"要推！！！"},{"pid":"82ea65760e0edefc4e2e2cbfd1333d0f333d1503","tid":1424800,"uid":37753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:04:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"631504874d2407e29de2d66be9c17d4bee6b4522","tid":1424800,"uid":47548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"應對被扣港獨帽子既策略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423846</a>"},{"pid":"68d3520ac352cc5adbf9a880b67e4b166c93c3c2","tid":1424800,"uid":119779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"唔識PR 野<br />\n睇落有文有路"},{"pid":"9c7d98c6ecb9a35ef5ffadf30f8adbc18c9d3ff4","tid":1424800,"uid":298635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9137af180485f8bc0c81b7f2ba2d1ca979ec8d21","tid":1424800,"uid":22423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:14:13.000Z","msg":"劉明一身蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c462826134df1eda67fe247dc8f1750838d08bf3","tid":1424800,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4945310612d5635634eafe89a329bee3fdf8c3f","tid":1424800,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb6ee70ce0628656c33a16968f5a7fd91f34f84","tid":1424800,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:55:00.000Z","msg":"佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"86517cb0a0174b2c9f9a0295bdbe5a9fbc729cd7","tid":1424800,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:58:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c52ca90170b19fe4156c6e6a4ab149354847580","tid":1424800,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 期待佢地上黎徵召人手"},{"pid":"b9c4ba659dd15c8de0557ff1fcdb3dbf9bb375cf","tid":1424800,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138e527d9300a10d016743fb449b949c16492c4a","tid":1424800,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:17:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ae1802b2b9f488c016e60269059480eb8959446","tid":1424800,"uid":22423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fae595b98548ff2f83d5cc8a436eaac13af043","tid":1424800,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5491f76d8e9d0e57b2b4d8c9d12c7de39148216","tid":1424800,"uid":258602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:18:41.000Z","msg":"[找亮點]到底係狗扮暴徒定有黑社會扮狗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425838</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同浸大學生會會長有關！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry for標題差"},{"pid":"b0e728bcbf44662c7720dde7a7cc05fd2b1611a2","tid":1424800,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d50a57b993b599d60a1f521e92b546ad7944a349","tid":1424800,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好野一推"},{"pid":"c064fff6bfc849736fd85cb1e01f8b25d335ab1c","tid":1424800,"uid":293281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42fc4327e2759029d1f0572ed0b2eb2d27bfe43f","tid":1424800,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"483ede4c2f1990307129ba22b645f3d8445ca0d9","tid":1424800,"uid":39412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n未講正題前首先背十次: 記者會講到頭其實都係點SPIN點SET AGENDA</strong><br />\n<br />\n人邊個冇BIASE?成見? 話冇都係呃你, 記者一樣, 兩個月來時態呢度好多人會有種&rdquo;記者大多數, 即使唔係全部, 都同情我地&rdquo;的感覺, 不過可以講比大家知, 一定唔係, 你放料, 佢&rdquo;睇情況編輯&rdquo;再出, 全香港人不可能同時現場聽你講, 點都係&rdquo;食二手飯&rdquo;, 你點現場控制訊息好關鍵.<br />\n<br />\n點叫&rdquo;持平&rdquo;, 十個人有十種認知, 冇一種&rdquo;持平&rdquo;係大多數人都接受, 做到80%持平已經唔錯.<br />\n<br />\n記實後, 點冇大台都好, 都需要有一個TEAM準備材料, 包括聲明, SOUNDBITE, 回應口徑<br />\n<br />\n當年老細講明, 開得PRESS EVENT, 一定要大家有清晰目的<br />\n<br />\n好似可以定調為:<br />\n<strong>&rdquo;三位(或N位)有親歷近日活動參與者, 以第一身經歷披露多日心路歷程(舉例), 我唔代表所有人, 只就自己所見同傳媒朋友&rdquo;分享</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>現在政府正式開動公關機器, 就係要將戴黃帽全黑妖魔化, 你地要做就係反制, 比番媒介一個有血有肉面孔</strong><br />\n可以冇大台, 但決定正式記者會就都要有一組人在背後做MEDIA TEAM<br />\n工作如下：<br />\n１．擬定聲明，用番會出來見記者幾位朋友自己名義，就你可披露自己個人身份程度來分享自己心聲<br />\n２．度下ＳＯＵＮＤＢＩＴＥ， 一Ｄ吸引到媒介引用甚至做標題句子，好似 &quot;齊上齊落，為香港自由未來奮鬥;由反送中起，到鞏固民主為止&quot; `之類<br />\n3. 當然你地唔會好似商業機構拍公關公司，有固定media manager，但每次最好都有幾位代表，負責聯絡記者，同記者溝通，人可以次次不同，但呢個位一定要有，亦可以晌保障出記者會同道私隱前提下代表佢地同記者聯繫<br />\n<br />\n既然全球賣廣告都做到，搵幾位冇參與前面，唔驚會隨時被拉的面孔出現，可以做到比一個面孔比媒介睇, the business of PR is about perception, 入行鬼婆老細格言<br />\n<br />\n然後就係Media training，你唔可以到個日先膽粗粗上場等記者問，預先度晒有可能出現問題，再搵其他人幫手操一次，包括最冒犯性最難聽的問題，反覆度好最見得人答案，呢步不能不做，否則在記者媒介前好易出事<br />\n<br />\n到左個日，最好有一位可以出樣的做MC，引導流程再安排記者問問題，近來咁多直播，睇多幾次就應該識，不多講<br />\n<br />\n今次見大家比人挑戰代表性問題，既然係心聲分享，就守實我地只係分享個人所見，不代表全部示威者的底線，777都係咁然硬守條 line，再問就話因為我地兩個月來太多感想，想由第一身身份同公眾講說話<br />\n<br />\n同場最好有同伴負責全程錄音，呢種係標準記者會動作，以防比人亂寫或曲解<br />\n<br />\n現在網絡咁發達，當然網上不會有一個示威者&quot;官網&quot;，但可以同步制作自已一方角度影片，經個人或其他渠道發放分享，可以同時平衡傳統媒介報導，要同步<br />\n<br />\n記者會後唔係就咁算數，今次負責媒介的&quot;文宣&quot;最好電郵比出席記者感謝佢地出席，如果可行重可以留低聯絡方式比佢地續問，咁先至係禮成，如果之後可以有人keep不同報導反映內容角度更佳<br />\n<br />\n小小心得，唔知大家用唔用得著<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:30:22.000Z","msg":"想請教用D小恩小惠對記者有冇用? <br />\n例如開場前派下野食, 野飲? 關心下入左院D記者情況?"}]}